node.text:
🌷💕✨🌼
If I could give any advice to young creatives out there it’s take your damn time. Everyone on social media moves at the speed of light because we aren’t seeing the times where people are resting, learning, falling & getting back up again. We are only ever seeing the final results. I’ve always been the type who needed years to complete projects. There is a certain level of patience you have to have with yourself to get to the finish line. Just know that whatever speed it takes you to get there is the exact speed the universe intended for you. 💗

node.text:
🍄💕🌙 
In my little cave of creation, isolated for a month in Hawaii. Writing a film and album I feel destined to make. No human interaction, just killing dead parts of myself to make room for the new. 
✨✨✨✨
When I create it is the only time the past,
present and future all meet me at once. Releasing past feelings from past moments and past lives, by keeping the channel open/antenna out in the present, to be able to co-create with the universe something that will be felt, seen, and heard in the future. 

Until then 🧚🏼‍♀️

node.text:
💗🎂🍄🧚🏼‍♀️✨🌙
Direction/Costume design/styling/ by me 

Choreography: @brianfriedman
Hair: @williamscottblair 
Makeup: @mugopus + @devanellemua 
Dancers: @allthatjasss @tiffanyaliyah @izverdea 
Band: @bonstarr @littleliska @thaddeusdixon 
Video content producer: @segijo 
Production designer: @butchallen1 
Camera director: @emma.westenberg 

+ So many amazing dedicated souls worked on this streamed show. super grateful to get to work with such lovely humans. 

Thank you all for a beautiful era filled with growth, love, creativity and magic! Time to write the next chapter💗🧚🏼‍♀️
